Jake gets his wish.

But things aren''t quite as simple as they seem. Just because the Animorphs no longer exist doesn''t mean the Yeerks no longer exist. Except now Jake, Rachel, Tobias, Cassie, and Marco can''t morph. They don''t even know the Yeerks are out there. And it''s not such a wonderful life...', 'In an alternate take on the Animorphs saga, Jake wishes away their powers and the team''s formation, thrusting the kids into a Yeerk-invaded world without morphing abilities.', 2000, '0439173078', '9780613242042', 179, NULL, 221, 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/12386595-L.jpg', '/works/OL8116375W', NULL, 'March 2001', 'English', NULL, 1, 0, 'back-to-before-katherine-applegate', 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 'public', '2026-03-16 21:28:10', '2026-03-22 20:32:05');
