That''s when things go terribly wrong. Before they know it, Jake, the Animorphs, and Ax find themselves in another place. Another time. And there''s no way home...', 'Jake and the Animorphs hijack a crashed alien ship to expose the Yeerk invasion, but a malfunction strands them in a mysterious jungle in another time.', 1997, '0439014239', '9783473348619', 162, NULL, NULL, 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/12649463-L.jpg', '/works/OL8115229W', NULL, 'January 1, 1999', 'English', NULL, 1, 0, 'the-forgotten-katherine-applegate', 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 'public', '2026-03-16 21:28:57', '2026-03-22 20:32:05');
